;\">下月舉行的區議會選舉難以有公平性</span>，有助選團亦擔心在街上工作時被襲擊，希望政府審慎考慮各方面的可能性。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2270349/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2270349%2F&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=90d3199f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2270349/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:48:57.000Z","msg":"咁我哋拆香港01、公平啦？"},{"pid":"0cd19b648d6dd521a7d45c7dc035ea131a152fde","tid":1638280,"uid":285794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a45ca156bd0b5d9757b00c0cd2c03a6c049db5c","tid":1638280,"uid":164374,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"特首都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"警總<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d13bde81d7a99db7a25fb3b3cf3d5356fdbeac","tid":1638280,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"林卓廷早排咪俾人淋完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6141165cfbc5d37ab2639f4d115a8c9b0d2403","tid":1638280,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20160216/large/1455599556_a403.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20160216%2Flarge%2F1455599556_a403.png&h=0a9c7b9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc1a1c09bb4b0ff467025a5d809a43b54eda812f","tid":1638280,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"冇睇新聞？<br />\n毛ee辦事處咪比人淋過紅油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泛民議員比人打過呀"},{"pid":"24d8da196b2d842c2b58e086c54a1e44ae822cc2"